// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2218 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 87911afd-1c47-5330-9dce-717c06405ce9

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:4.0*")
